Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.97,0:00:03.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:07.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make \Nsure to keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.18,0:00:09.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:13.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:18.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazingly, it turns out Lucy is the daughter of the Heartfilia Konzern!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.51,0:00:20.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How surprising...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.31,0:00:27.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom Lord was after her, but thanks to the master invoking Fairy Law, our battle with them is finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:29.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:53.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right! I'll yell it out countless times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:58.70,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe your every tomorrow will be shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:01.05,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The intersection of all people
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.05,0:01:03.66,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,whose dreams have come true is one point:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:08.29,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Never giving up.  And that's why we're not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:13.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,When it seems like you'll be blown away by the headwinds,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:15.62,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,grasp this hand, try to take a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:18.89,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're not alone anymore, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:24.00,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Go forward, more and more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:26.52,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up on your awesome dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:27.78,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:29.25,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Move on, my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:31.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, with the light shining down upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:33.71,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even think about something like giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:36.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you trade being hurt again for strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.14,0:01:41.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes, always looking straight ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:45.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,can surely see the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.03,0:02:08.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone seems really happy, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:09.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:13.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:18.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:24.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you hear me, Gajeel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:27.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:31.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So hey, where'd you learn Dragon Slayer magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:34.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I couldn't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:38.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never met anyone who used the same magic as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:40.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You could at least tell me that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:45.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Metalicana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:48.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Iron Dragon, Metalicana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:50.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:54.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! You were taught by a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:55.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:57.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So where is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:02:58.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:02.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:04.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I didn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:10.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:14.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just talkin' to you makes my brains turn to mush.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:16.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:19.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:25.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, Metalicana suddenly vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:28.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Without saying a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.23,0:03:31.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man... What a selfish jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:38.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that wasn't 7 years ago on July 7th, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:42.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Do you know where Metalicana is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:47.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance. I'm looking for Igneel, a fire dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:51.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He also disappeared 7 years ago on July 7th.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:53.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,7 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:57.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Year 777, Month 7, Day 7...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On that day two dragons disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it a bunch of sevens lined up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:03.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:08.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like I care anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:11.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're leavin', then scat already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:14.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is {\i1}our{\i0} guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:16.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that should get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, why so picky?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:23.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a call if you find anything about Igneel, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:27.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell should I be nice to you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:30.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're both Dragon Slayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:33.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that crap! Next time we meet, I'll kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:35.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:37.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you've said your prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:39.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dangerous, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:42.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we could call it even now and make up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:44.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:47.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at what you did to our guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:50.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you busted up our guild first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:53.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! I give up makin' nice with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:04.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They've really made a big mess now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:08.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:15.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've really had a tough time, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:17.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give us that face, Lu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:19.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:22.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:25.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone worked together to beat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:27.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although the guild was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:30.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We all just need to rebuild it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:31.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oui.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:35.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you worry, Lu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:38.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! This is all my...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:40.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:44.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But nobody thinks this is your fault, Lu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:48.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand... I'm sorry I couldn't be more help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:50.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:56.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fun things, sad things... We can't share everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:05:58.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but what we can, we should share...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:01.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means to be a guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A single person's happiness is everyone's happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:06.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A single person's anger is everyone's anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:10.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And a single person's tears are everyone's tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:14.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no reason to feel guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:20.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy... You should be able to tell how everyone feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:28.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:33.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're part of the Fairy Tail family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:55.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:57.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We went a bit overboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:07:00.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to seriously anger the Council...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:04.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or wait, if it goes poorly, maybe even imprisonment...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:07.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:10.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:14.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been one week since our battle with Phantom ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:19.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've finally gotten back our peaceful days...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:21.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, let's take a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:27.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although after it happened, it's been super tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:31.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were rounded up by the Council's army, the Rune Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:32.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:33.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They've already caught wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:34.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:36.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:40.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not going to work Natsu. You can't get away from the Rune Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:43.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:50.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were dragged to the army post to be interviewed about what had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:56.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day they'd question us, but finally after a week, it calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:08:03.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like Fairy Tail's punishment will be handed down from the Council at a later date.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:08.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, don't worry Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:12.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it'll be that bad of a punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:17.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the circumstantial evidence and witness reports all point to an attack from Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:23.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope these bruises goes away...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:36.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Mom... Do you think {\i1}he{\i0} was behind the whole thing, pulling the strings?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:39.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what he's like, but to go this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:47.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he'd do it. He wouldn't have any problem with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:53.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would he suddenly try and take me back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:56.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like he cares about me personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:06.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll do it again, won't he? Using the power of his money...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:08.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:11.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:17.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:20.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's 'cause you tried to carry so many at once, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:21.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:23.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:25.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're carrying them so daintily!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:28.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama, carry me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:29.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:32.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Less talking, more working!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:35.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to rebuild Fairy Tail ASAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:36.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza's really into it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:40.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She can requip to an outfit like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:43.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master's also really getting into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:45.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:48.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Foreman, where do you need this timber?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:49.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she calling foreman?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:54.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I hate losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:55.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, it's whack-a-mole!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:56.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:58.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it kind of big?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:10:01.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,While we're at it, we're expanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:03.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Here's what it'll look like when it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:04.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.09,0:10:05.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:07.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be fine without changing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:08.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of guild is it going to be like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:13.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is another...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:14.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:18.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But man, this is really crappy. What idiot drew this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was Mira-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:25.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You made her cry again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:27.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And such is Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:31.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Gray-sama is only kind to Juvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:36.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:36.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:38.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:39.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:41.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm soaked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:42.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lunch box!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:43.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A lunch box?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:48.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:52.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! This is called a character lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:54.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I actually eat something this insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:56.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dripping something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:57.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:11:01.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia is heartbroken! She took 3 days and nights straight to make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:03.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said you could eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:06.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that one of those character lunches?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:14.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't bad. Give me some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:16.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'll eat it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:18.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum! So delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:19.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat it everyday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:22.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means... Will you marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:24.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'll give you 30 babies or more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:26.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia's overwhelmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:28.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, Gray, Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:33.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you give these to Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:34.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're her keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:35.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:37.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering where you'd gone off to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:39.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been searching for these the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:42.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? You don't look good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:45.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:48.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... It's hard being a male feminist...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:53.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy isn't here. Her injuries hurt so bad she can't move, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:54.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should go check on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:55.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You come too, Loke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:57.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:12:01.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know I can't handle Celestial Wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:02.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Lucy's still Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:07.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu. We all have our weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:09.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:16.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Karen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:21.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Must you be in such a rush? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:26.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:27.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You feelin' okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come in through the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:32.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enter through the door, people. The door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:34.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:35.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:37.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:39.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd usually be all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:41.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:43.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.33,0:12:44.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:46.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, you perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:49.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like this was bound to happen eventually...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:50.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon the intrusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:51.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She ain't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:54.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how it's supposed to go! And get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:56.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:12:58.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come here, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:01.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your straight-man act is lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:03.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Without Lucy our tempo is all off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:07.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit finding fault! And oh, I'm so sorry I suck at comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:08.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:09.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:11.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you people doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:14.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's underwear like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Underwear? That?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:20.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When would you wear such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:21.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're eatin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:22.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, no how.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:23.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, this is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:25.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Close the drawer already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:27.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:29.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where have you been searching?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:34.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're these?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:36.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:40.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I finally joined the guild of my dreams, Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't go reading those!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.97,0:13:49.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I met a person named Erza. She's cool and pretty. Then Natsu and Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:52.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these all letters to her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:53.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:55.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why she didn't send them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:56.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She left a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:13:59.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Lucy left a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:01.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"I will go home."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:02.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:06.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:20.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! I made your face on a rice ball, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:25.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it! Eat up and work hard, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:28.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working. I'll deal with you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:30.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:33.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll leave it right here. Eat it later, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:35.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you see, today it's, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:40.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you not hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:41.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:49.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:52.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said you were bothering me, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:54.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our personal chef cooks our food!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:15:00.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time to do that, then you have time to learn something about running an empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:02.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand? Now leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:06.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Today is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:09.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...my birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:17.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Spetto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:23.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Madame Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:29.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're okay, Madame L... Madame L...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:31.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for worrying everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:37.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M'lady, we have some new reference books from the East...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:40.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M'lady, how you've grown... Run off with a lover or two have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:45.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been keeping up with your magic studies?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:46.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we get to see you again, M'lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:48.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There go the waterworks...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:51.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all the same as ever, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:56.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M'lady... M'lord asks you come to the study at the main residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:03.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He tells his daughter that ran away and came back to report to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:06.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't changed either, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:13.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forgotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:18.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I lived here, I would wear clothes like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:20.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it too tight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:23.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten a little small for you, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:24.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:28.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah... I've gotten taller...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:32.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:38.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Lucy. I have returned, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:39.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:46.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you have finally returned, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:49.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:53.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for running away from home without saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:56.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I truly regret those actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:59.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have made a wise decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:07.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you are in that guild, I must use my wealth and influence to crush it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:12.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have finally matured, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:20.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I've made you realize how much trouble your selfish actions cause for those around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:25.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the daughter of the Heartfilias.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:27.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not like other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:30.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You live in different worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:34.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is fortunate that you finally understand this, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:40.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is only one reason I've had you returned. A very fortunate event.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:44.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A marriage with the son of the Jurener family has been proposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:48.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I figured it was something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:55.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A marriage with the Jurener family will allow the Heartfilia Railways to make solid strides to the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:18:00.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This marriage with ensure our future fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:02.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our fortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:05.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you must give birth to a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:07.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So he can become heir to the Heartfilia estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:10.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:14.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:16.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:22.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have returned in order to show you my resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:26.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I was wrong to leave without saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:30.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was no different than simply running way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:34.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this time, I'm going to tell you exactly how I feel before I leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:37.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:40.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing fortunate about having your fate decided for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:42.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You must grab your own happiness yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:44.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to walk my own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:47.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go deciding on who I'll marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:49.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:52.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not lay a finger on Fairy Tail again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:01.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:06.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...I, and everyone else in the guild, will consider you the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:13.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't done that, maybe we could be a bit more civil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:16.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's too late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:19.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have hurt my friends far too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:27.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What I want isn't money, or pretty dresses, or fortune forced upon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:32.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not Lucky Lucy of the Heartfilias any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:38.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail is my other family now, and they recognize me just as Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:41.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a far more loving family than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:46.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I only lived here a little while, but leaving the home I lived in with Mother was incredibly difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:52.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Spetto, Old Man Belo, Mr. Ribbon, Mrs. Aed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:56.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be really hard to leave them all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:19:57.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:19:59.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.89,0:20:03.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If Mom was still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:08.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she'd tell me "You go do what you want to do."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:10.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.49,0:20:15.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.48,0:20:28.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:38.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:40.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:42.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:44.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.56,0:21:15.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry I worried you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:18.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it's our fault for jumping to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:20.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we were worried for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:23.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy was crying the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:25.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were sobbing too, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:27.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:29.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:32.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But sheesh, what a spacious town.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:34.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so calm and peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:37.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this isn't a town. It's our garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:40.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our land goes all the way to that mountain over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:43.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:44.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:46.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail, Princess Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:47.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Said it like it's nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:50.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu and Gray have been beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:52.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Erza, please, give your orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:56.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky sure is blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:22:00.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Erza's malfunctioning!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.53,0:22:09.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To Mom up in Heaven, I'm doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:17.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what Mom? I don't think I can live without my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.13,0:22:23.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Fairy Tail is already a part of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.49,0:24:01.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All we've been doing is fighting lately... We'd better do some jobs, or we're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:05.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's some rough job with a good reward that you can do, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.18,0:24:07.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do delicate work, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.83,0:24:09.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not your style.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.11,0:24:11.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty then, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.74,0:24:12.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your style!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.61,0:24:14.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to repeat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.37,0:24:16.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Next Generation!
